{"tid":1349920,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[能不能接受?] 官方COS不同凡響！ 《幽遊白書》舞台劇10大角色定妝照","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T14:31:52.000Z","uid":75050,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65959926962a979bb46e92c8f659245c8d7b4158","tid":1349920,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:30:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2384975215106319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2384975215106319&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKj4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=8d320820\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2384975215106319</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YeKMxJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YeKMxJ.jpg&h=292e15d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【其他】官方COS不同凡響！ 《幽遊白書》舞台劇10大角色定妝照辣眼<br />\n<br />\n  島國的人氣ACG已經有無數名作都被搬上了舞台劇，而7月22日今天，曾經的不朽名作《幽遊白書》（YuYuHakuSho）新舞台劇10大角色定妝照公佈，官方COS，造型逼真，氣度不凡。<br />\n<br />\n  《幽遊白書》是日本漫畫家富堅義博的代表名作，曾與《七龍珠》（Dargon Ball）、《灌籃高手》（Slam Dunk）一同並列為1990年代《周刊少年Jump》（Magazine Shonen JUMP）的三大代表漫畫，其漫畫後期飄逸抽象的畫風姑且不論，其精彩劇情設定奠定了富堅老賊在漫畫界的傲嬌不二地位。<br />\n<br />\n  最新《幽遊白書》舞台劇4大基友角色人選已經公開，浦飯幽助由山崎翼飾演、桑原和真由鄉本直也飾演、藏馬由鈴木擴樹飾演、飛影由橋本祥平飾演，預定8月東京開演，敬請期待吧。<br />\n<br />\n  本次公佈的10大角色定妝照分別為：4大基友幽助、桑原、藏馬和飛影，4大美女雪村螢子、幻海、牡丹和浦飯溫子，另外2位則是小閻王和剛鬼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8iqepjo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8iqepjo.png&h=9169fda6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28CgCEp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28CgCEp.png&h=4c2b8f5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qsO7Kjp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqsO7Kjp.png&h=189cee5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REXPXEq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREXPXEq.png&h=52117162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/db5BCEq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdb5BCEq.png&h=5021593e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PeDGOL6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPeDGOL6.png&h=c4576831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a8DcaZs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa8DcaZs.png&h=655ea2b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8tHwrxO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8tHwrxO.png&h=62ed9201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMG9dcP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMG9dcP.png&h=4029c7dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJ78tL9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJ78tL9.png&h=966135a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c129c5ca648132c33b3f0f7121da79fdc99693bf","tid":1349920,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f636b5e76d14963028a378935ba155fb5a03ebd6","tid":1349920,"uid":122471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:58:41.000Z","msg":"d女+飛影個頭幾高質, btw, 幽助係邊? 唔係主角咩? 舞台劇冇佢份定點"},{"pid":"9f6397980a97cc24b3531e7025158e26d1884bd0","tid":1349920,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f636b5e76d14963028a378935ba155fb5a03ebd6","tid":1349920,"uid":122471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:58:41.000Z","msg":"d女+飛影個頭幾高質, btw, 幽助係邊? 唔係主角咩? 舞台劇冇佢份定點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c376d96af1b3e8200d9fc7a604feb562bb3fef2","tid":1349920,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s